Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Pol Pot regime falls
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bwfx
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 14 Jan 1979
Cambodia's Pol Pot regime toppled by Vietnamese incursion. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.